                    ngettext(
                        "Message moved to %s",
                        "Messages moved to %s",
                        messages.size
                    ).printf(destination.get_display_name()),
                    undone_tooltip
                );
            }

            yield context.commands.execute(command, context.cancellable);
        }
    }

